{"tid":1592793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《紐約時報》訪問三名811當晚 遭臥底打至重傷被捕者　傷勢包括：肩關節骨碎成四塊，腦出血，門牙飛脫","createTime":"2019-09-24T18:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T20:14:46.000Z","uid":3893,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"43dbd8777ef403ae28f1842faeafe1f5f20af2a6","tid":1592793,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T18:47:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DoMO5o9z2WQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDoMO5o9z2WQ&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=7a2b5f5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DoMO5o9z2WQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警方在持續近四個月的「反送中」運動中，疑對被捕者濫用暴力，備受外界批評。8 月 11 日在銅鑼灣，首次有警員被傳媒發現喬裝成示威者，制服並逮捕多名示威者，當晚有 15 人被捕，其中數人嚴重受傷。《紐約時報》訪問其中三名被捕者，當中有人被警員打至門牙脫落，被警員用警棍毆打及踩臉，事後因出血而每天也會流鼻血，更有人被警員「飛撲」壓倒，導致肩關節骨碎成四塊。其中一名受訪者將申請民事索償。<br />\n<br />\n當晚有傳媒拍到多名蒙面、喬裝成示威者的警員，衝至希慎廣場對出把數名示威者大力按在地，並以警棍毆打，片段其後在網上瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》分析當晚片段，與十多名目擊者、示威者和專家進行訪談，周日（22日）刊出報道，三名當晚遭逮捕的男子戴上口罩，在鏡頭前接受訪問。<br />\n <br />\n立場新聞報導：<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/811-%E9%81%AD%E5%96%AC%E8%A3%9D%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85%E8%82%A9%E9%97%9C%E7%AF%80%E9%AA%A8%E7%A2%8E%E6%88%90%E5%9B%9B%E5%A1%8A-%E8%85%A6%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%80-%E9%96%80%E7%89%99%E9%A3%9B%E8%84%AB-%E5%82%B7%E5%8F%A3%E8%A2%AB%E5%99%B4%E6%A4%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F811-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2596%25AC%25E8%25A3%259D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%2582%25A9%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25AF%2580%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E7%25A2%258E%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25A1%258A-%25E8%2585%25A6%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%2580-%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%2589%2599%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%2584%25AB-%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25A4%2592%2F&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=23cd9df6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F811-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2596%25AC%25E8%25A3%259D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%2582%25A9%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25AF%2580%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E7%25A2%258E%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25A1%258A-%25E8%2585%25A6%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%2580-%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%2589%2599%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%2584%25AB-%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25A4%2592%2F&h=99cb2fec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/811-%E9%81%AD%E5%96%AC%E8%A3%9D%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85%E8%82%A9%E9%97%9C%E7%AF%80%E9%AA%A8%E7%A2%8E%E6%88%90%E5%9B%9B%E5%A1%8A-%E8%85%A6%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%80-%E9%96%80%E7%89%99%E9%A3%9B%E8%84%AB-%E5%82%B7%E5%8F%A3%E8%A2%AB%E5%99%B4%E6%A4%92/</a></span>"},{"pid":"46f38b1649269a22cae40e2decfe10ac4c52d81c","tid":1592793,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T18:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"215824744eeabdebd256562d1b4b67cb7ac67452","tid":1592793,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T18:48:28.000Z","msg":"like and share 先<br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba51f718cdb05d8266fd0ded1b012ae0be6de1b8","tid":1592793,"ui